- POST schedule monthly service

POST body:
- customerId
- scheduledDate
- preferredTime
- assignedTechnicianUserId
- assignedTechnicianName
- priority
- notes

POST behavior:
- Auth admin/superadmin/manager only.
- Validates customer exists.
- schedule_month is first day of current month.
- service_type is MONTHLY_SERVICE.
- status is ASSIGNED when technician info exists, otherwise SCHEDULED.
- Duplicate customer/month/service_type active schedules return 409 with: This customer is already scheduled for this month.

