Implementation notes:
- /Admindashboard More section Reports button routes to /admin/reports using router.push.
- /Admindashboard KPI grid has a Reports Quality card that routes to /admin/reports using router.push.
- No window.open is used.
- The reports page is mobile-card-first with desktop/tablet horizontal table fallback.
- The reports page loading state uses metric, mobile-card, and desktop-table skeletons that match the report data shape.
- The dashboard does not fetch /api/admin/reports/summary. Report DB queries run only when the reports page opens.
- /api/admin/reports/summary has a short in-memory cache so repeat opens/refreshes do not repeatedly hit the DB.
- AMC/Warranty due date parsing is defensive because the customer table has invalid text dates such as 31/11/2026. Invalid date text is treated as null for expiry calculations instead of crashing the report.

