Passkey API rules:
- All passkey APIs are POST only.
- Registration APIs require existing logged-in user from getUserFromRequest.
- Login options can accept username or allow discoverable passkey login if username is empty.
- Challenges expire in 5 minutes.
- Delete expired challenges before creating a new challenge.
- Delete used challenges after verification.
- Do not cache passkey API responses.
- Service worker must not cache passkey/auth APIs.
- Use the same cookie security settings as the existing password login API.

